  "description": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">只要上大学，就要考四六级。但其实，毕业后</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">找工作时，用人单位会综合考虑许多因素，</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你会发现这些证书比四六级还重要。</span></p>\n\n<section label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下面就跟着阁主（ID：hujiangcet）一起来看下，有哪些证书吧！</span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">01</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">毕业证、学位证</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xcGljLmNuL21tYml6X2pwZy9pYTZwOUNYblViZmYweGJ3c25aOWlhMkRDak1mSHA5dGxBWTZkU2dPaWNiUEdBdlp2eVByRzJ1SkN1V0JPY1dNQ2lhNlo4aHpuczJSWW85VngzT1BMRkd3eUEvMD93eF9mbXQ9anBlZw==\" style=\"white-space: normal;\" /></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">虽说企业更看重能力，而不是学历，但名牌大学、名校热门专业，就是一块极具分量的敲门砖，如果还拥有第二学位，那只会让你在求职过程时如虎添翼。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">02</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">英语证书</span></strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 1;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); padding-right: 2px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 2px;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 0.3em 0.4em; line-height: 1; text-align: center; border-radius: 80% 100% 90% 20%; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); color: rgb(255, 255, 240);\">\n<section>1</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 0.4em; color: #2F8A4D; line-height: 1.4;\">四六级证书 </span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">大学英语四、六级成绩(CET-4，CET-6)，极其重要；</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span>大学英语四、六级口语成绩：重要；</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span>2016年起，四六级考试改革后，成绩单发生如下变化：</span></p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n<section style=\"padding-bottom: 1.2em;\">\n<section><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; font-size: 80px; line-height: 1em; color: #C0C8D1;\">&ldquo;</span>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; clear: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1. 笔试和口试的成绩在同一份成绩报告单上报道，不再单独颁发口语考试成绩报告单。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left; clear: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2.考生取得笔试和口试其中一项有效成绩，均发放成绩报告单。</span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; height: 1em; float: right; line-height: 1;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 4em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209);\">&nbsp;</section>\n<span>&rdquo;</span></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span>参加2017年6月四六级考试的你，将会收到如下四六级成绩单：</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei9pYTZwOUNYblViZmYweGJ3c25aOWlhMkRDak1mSHA5dGxBcE5CVjdDSndvR1pzZ3lvVEphOERYc3cyQ0N4aWNnaWJxWVJyQ1MyNFVlSGh5czd2NHFTOHNITWcvMD93eF9mbXQ9b3RoZXI=\" /></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">成绩单比证书更直观地显示了个体的差异。因此，阁主建议想进银行、公务员或外企的同学，四六级成绩在550分以上，才更具竞争力。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n<section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); font-size: 14px; padding-left: 15px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>特别提醒：</strong></span></p>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">四级多次刷分不过，特别是成绩在350分以下，最终目标想要拿下六级的考生，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">你们的语法、词汇都有很大问题。</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">需要把基础打扎实了，再进行四六级考试</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\">题型技巧强化训练</strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">阁主推荐你们先使用新概念经典教材打基础，再开黑四六级，双管齐下，更有效！</span></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/course/5417082?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: center;\">【Uni智能】英语零基础直达大学六级【全额奖学金班】&gt;&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #666666; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;\">经典教材，智能高效新学法&middot;由浅入深，稳步提升更轻松</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #006400;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">&darr;戳图直达&darr;</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/course/5417082?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/hjclass/public/upload/201708/bd8fe618-9df8-46cc-98b8-7fc4a22f83b1.jpg\" /></a></p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n<section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); padding-left: 15px;\">\n<p><strong>限时优惠：</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">报名该全额奖学金班的学员，在规定时间达到规定学完率，即可得到学币返还，返还额度都以扣除学习卡、优惠券、折扣、订单立减等优惠的最终实付金额为基准。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #888888;\">（具体时间及学完率规定，学币返还规则进班后可在班级讨论区查看）</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 1;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); padding-right: 2px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 2px;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 0.3em 0.4em; line-height: 1; text-align: center; border-radius: 80% 100% 90% 20%; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); color: rgb(255, 255, 240);\">\n<p>2</p>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 0.4em; color: #2F8A4D; line-height: 1.4;\">剑桥商务英语（BEC） </span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">BEC证书有&ldquo;外企通行证&rdquo;、&ldquo;外企绿卡&rdquo;之称，是全球求职英语能力证明的首选证书。很多企业的招聘考试采用了BEC考试题目，它是进入西门子、普华永道、强生等500强公司的一块敲门砖，<span style=\"color: #006400;\">且一旦考取，</span></span><span style=\"color: #006400;\">各个级别考试证书<strong>终身有效</strong>。&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">相对于报名费15~80元的四六级考试，BEC考试报名费如下：</span></p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n<section style=\"padding-bottom: 1.2em;\">\n<section><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; font-size: 80px; line-height: 1em; color: #C0C8D1;\">&ldquo;</span>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; clear: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2016-2017年度BEC初级考试费为465元人民币/人；</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left; clear: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">BEC中级考试费为580元人民币/人；</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left; clear: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">BEC高级考试费为725元人民币/人。</span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; height: 1em; float: right; line-height: 1;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 4em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209);\">&nbsp;</section>\n<span>&rdquo;</span></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">对自己的四六级成绩不满意，而又因学校限制无法再报考四六级的同学，不妨选择BEC考试。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n<section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); padding-left: 15px;\">\n<p><strong>考试级别推荐：</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">推荐考试级别：BEC中级（一般专业够用）或BEC高级（更高追求者建议尝试）。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">如果<span>不知道自己目前的水平能报考什么级别，可参考下方表格：</span></span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9wbmcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZmMHhid3NuWjlpYTJEQ2pNZkhwOXRsQUh5ZUNaZWljanVsN3FiTnR5YzlMazNoRmd0SDh0YlZmZGQ1N1F4VnJPM2pCQnR5U25OVDNzZ1EvMD93eF9mbXQ9cG5n\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">阁主要在这里提醒大家：</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">并不是说你考到了四级高分就能通过BEC中级，考到了六级高分就能过BEC高级，毕竟BEC考试内容<span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #2F8A4D;\"><strong>侧重商务环境，注重商务词汇及表述</strong></span>，和四六级的考查范围还是有所区分。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">且BEC考试口语必考，平时不开口，考试时临场发挥是行不通的。想要对得起报名费，还是要稳打稳扎，找针对性的书籍和资料进行复习。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">阁主推荐<a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/12358437290?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #2F8A4D;\">沪江网校BEC智能强化课程&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a>，限时特价，全额返还奖学金！助力拿下BEC高级，为你提升职场&ldquo;证&rdquo;能量！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #006400;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">&darr;戳图直达&darr;</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/12358437290?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZmMHhid3NuWjlpYTJEQ2pNZkhwOXRsQXlFWXp0WHdxVW53V2xrSEJhclJDUjREbXRhMUxpY0JTREJPSlhoQTdQTHJqMENhQTJFYUUwNEEvMD93eF9mbXQ9anBlZw==\" /></a></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 1;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); padding-right: 2px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 2px;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 0.3em 0.4em; line-height: 1; text-align: center; border-radius: 80% 100% 90% 20%; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); color: rgb(255, 255, 240);\">\n<p>3</p>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 0.4em; color: #2F8A4D; line-height: 1.4;\">专四专八 </span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">英专生必备；考了专八<span style=\"color: #006400;\">基本就站在英语考试鄙视链的顶端了（当然翻译类资格证书除外）</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2018年英语专四考试时间：2018年4月21日；</span></strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2018年英语专八考试时间：2018年3月17日。&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">报名工作于2017年11月中旬到12月展开。</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n<section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); padding-left: 15px;\">\n<p><strong>非英语专业能报考吗？</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">很多同学问&ldquo;不是英语专业可以报考专四专八吗？&rdquo;答案是可以的。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">原则上专四专八只对英语专业以及英语相关专业开放，<strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #2F8A4D;\">但有的院校是允许六级优秀或是良好的考生报考的。</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #000000;\">所以请大家关注你们学校专四专八考试报名条件哦~&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2016年专四专八考试也改革了。<span style=\"color: #006400;\">写作难度上升</span>，听力部分考查方式跟四六级一样，题目不会出现在试卷上了，<span style=\"color: #006400;\"><strong>需要预读选项</strong></span>，这无疑增加了考试难度，渴望一次过级的同学，建议跟着老师学习，过级更有保障！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>推荐课程：</strong><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/12408434013?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\">英语专业八级（TEM8）备考【随到随学班】&gt;&gt;</a>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/12408434013?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\">英语专业四级（TEM4）备考【随到随学班】&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://f2n.c.hjfile.cn/pic/201506/29f72486-205d-4006-ae70-cd1485d9946f_n.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 1;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); padding-right: 2px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 2px;\">\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 0.3em 0.4em; line-height: 1; text-align: center; border-radius: 80% 100% 90% 20%; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); color: rgb(255, 255, 240);\">\n<p>4</p>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 0.4em; color: #2F8A4D; line-height: 1.4;\">翻译、中高级口译 </span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">立志投身翻译、外贸行业的同学，可以挑战翻译资格考试证书，一般可选CATTI翻译资格考试和上海的中高级口译考试。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有同学不大了解这两个考试的区别，阁主来科普下：</span></p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">上海的中高级口译考试</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">难度适度，比较<span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #2F8A4D;\"><strong>适合初学者去挑战一下自己</strong></span>，而且考试的内容也比较灵活，考生经过严格、科学的培训应该比较容易上手。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">上海的口译考试也<strong>不强调专业性</strong>，因为毕竟是面向社会各行各业的考试，还是要以大众为主，考题也主要是泛泛的内容，<strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #2F8A4D;\">强调基本表达和基本功的测试。</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/hjclass/public/upload/201709/f772b984-3278-41a2-9611-fe607eb5c748.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/133481576816?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\">推荐想要挑战自我的同学，跟着网校名师一起学习，过级更有保障哦&gt;&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">CATTI二级考试</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">难度要略高于上海高口。<span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #2F8A4D;\"><strong>二级是选优导向的职业性考试。</strong></span>CATTI三级比较适合大二、大三的学生报考，而二级则适合大四、研究生或在职翻译人员报考。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #2F8A4D;\">更具体的区别可以看图啦&darr;</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZmMHhid3NuWjlpYTJEQ2pNZkhwOXRsQTZXeUluQkswQWljNFV4MVh4WWQ1YjRKYzdVTnQ3bUNqWUt4aWNOVmlickdvaWJpYUNWcFdDOFV2dFh3LzA/d3hfZm10PWpwZWc=\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/12368437945?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\">CATTI考试通过后不仅颁发国家认证的资格证书，而且跟职称评定挂钩。市面上没有历年真题，考试时可以携带字典，但是难度高，需要跟着专业的老师学习、备考和实战&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">总结：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对比了这些考试的报名费，四六级考试性价比最高，而又能直接证明你的英语能力。大家一定要不遗余力冲高分！其他证书请按需考取哦~&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">03</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">计算机等级证书</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZmMHhid3NuWjlpYTJEQ2pNZkhwOXRsQUtqNE9SMGQxVHR1VHBoOUViU09iUWVLbmFpYzFXMjJqVW41aWFJVFU0VUdEalR6bHM1T0FSanZBLzA/d3hfZm10PWpwZWc=\" /></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/course/search?k=%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\">更多详情和充电请戳我&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">计算机重要性不言而喻。计算机专业同学更不用说，必须追求高等级通过。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Office操作已经成为职场必备技能，虽然不需要证书，但确是必须要会的。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">计算机二级证书：有些大城市申请户口时用，必要条件，如上海市。</span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其他如：ACCP、MCSA、CCNA，以及名目繁多的专项技能计算机证书，则与未来具体的工作选择相关，不是每个企业都会看重。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">04</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">学校荣誉证书</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZlaWJpYmZUQk55TnpJVkJlN3I1SE1odVpDYWgyTzhpYmlhVmg3WGpYS2JlblN6R1RxTFgxTzlnWTBsY3lLaWNKQ1k5THNndjh2aWE5bm1vdkl3LzA/d3hfZm10PWpwZWc=\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; width: auto !important; float: left;\" width=\"auto\" /></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">学校荣誉证书大致有这些：奖学金证书、三好学生、优秀毕业生、优秀学生干部&hellip;&hellip;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">奖学金证书证明你的学习能力。<span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;优秀学生干部&rdquo;的证书，说明你的沟通、协调、组织能力不错，相关岗位需要以上能力的话，给</span>HR留下的第一印象就会不错。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>而<span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">优秀毕业生，在申请<span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">(上海)</span>户口时候可以加分，非常重要。</span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">05</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">第二外语证书</span></strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">第二外语证书是加分项啦~ 别人没有，你有，大大增加了进入外贸比重很大的企业的机会。我们来看下面一组数据：</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">日语(世界500强中有87家日本企业)</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">法语(世界500强中<span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">有</span>36家法国企业)</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">德语(世界500强中<span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">有</span>35家德国企业)</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">韩语(世界500强中13家韩国企业)</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">据（网络）最新统计数据，其他如葡萄牙语、西班牙语、意大利语、阿拉伯语&hellip;&hellip;，</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当今中国与阿拉伯国家的石油合作、与南美国家的经济贸易，越来越频繁，这些小语种前景很被看好。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/131654612018?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\">2017年各大专业就业月薪TOP1是西班牙语哦</a>~ </span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/hjclass/2017/07/04/4de756e749270039cb58718bef801f66.png\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/12618434668?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\">赶紧学习一门二外吧&gt;&gt;</a></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">06</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">财务会计类证书</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZlaWJpYmZUQk55TnpJVkJlN3I1SE1odVowUVZoR2ZYNE54TWh2NHljN3lWTWdkeUtDMzVvQk4wNUozZnp5RURIYkt4bExpYWpKWTVtcThBLzA/d3hfZm10PWpwZWc=\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; width: auto !important;\" width=\"auto\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">注册会计师(CPA)：<strong>财会届具高含金量证书之一</strong>，具备大专及以上学历证书就可以报名参加。</span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 26.6667px;\">特许公认会计师(ACCA)：ACCA国际注会被称为&ldquo;会计师界的金饭碗&rdquo;。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">注册金融分析师(CFA)：需要相关方面3年以上工作经验，考证难度很高，费用也高，当然含金量也高。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://class.hujiang.com/category/12918434668?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=bee608f2\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更多财会类证书科普、介绍和课程，请戳这里&gt;&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">07</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(47, 138, 77); line-height: 1.6;\">专业资格证书</strong></span></p>\n</section>\n\n<section><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZlaWJpYmZUQk55TnpJVkJlN3I1SE1odVpJMkxhQW9LVTFxVnk2UTZQNzNTWWNCWmlhS3R3MXg2b0FiN0MydHpXSEsxTmliU0ZoVmljaWNVbzZBLzA/d3hfZm10PWpwZWc=\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-size: 22px; background-position: 50% 50%; width: 556px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 424px !important;\" width=\"auto\" /></section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这个跟自己的专业与未来想从事的行业就关系很大，同学们可以根据自己实际情况来对待。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">律师资格证书：想当律师的学生;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">CAD工程师认证证书：机械、室内装饰、建筑行业;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">导游资格证书：国家有规定，导游人员持证上岗;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">人力资源从业资格证书;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">国家司法考试证书;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">驾驶证：不是当司机才需要，已经成了工作生活中必备的证啦。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">08</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">兼职实习证明</span></strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZlaWJpYmZUQk55TnpJVkJlN3I1SE1odVpJaWM2SFJXbGFXdTR4dERQZGVUOWRGTXBUS1JWS0lBamhCU3dtampNUTVld3lnNTBKMFh0MzV3LzA/d3hfZm10PWpwZWc=\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; width: auto !important; float: left;\" width=\"auto\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">拥有兼职实习证明，就是&ldquo;有工作经验&rdquo;的毕业生了。相关性高的工作经验对求职很有帮助~&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">再者，一些公司会直接留下实习期表现优异的实习生。<span style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">现在很多大学生都利用暑假去兼职和实习，在选择兼职工作时尽快明确自己想做什么，把自己的优势和所学与工作相得益彰，以后的工作也能如鱼得水哦~&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">09</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">发表论文、专利证书</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对于研究生来说，做过相关项目，撰写过有质量的相关论文，而且被EI/SCI收录，这些发表论文的证明，<strong>在找与专业相关的工作、申请读博、申请落户（上海）</strong>，会有相当大的帮助。</span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">另外，本科生或研究生在申请出国的时候，如果发表过高质量的论文，就更容易获得国外教授的青睐。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">专利证书，不仅说明你是个有创新思维、有智慧的大学生，而且在申请户口中会起加分作用。<strong>企业对专利证书也相当看重。</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<article style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px;\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section class=\"RankEditor\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; white-space: normal; border-style: none; border-color: initial; width: 5em; text-align: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin-left: 1em;\">\n<section style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; display: inline-block; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); width: 1.7em; height: 1.7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p class=\"count white\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">10</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">竞赛获奖证书</span></strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</article>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZlaWJpYmZUQk55TnpJVkJlN3I1SE1odVpLOUxJTXVKQ0Y1WWVxOExHZWlhdGRZTjNMdWM5MjE1M3JlbmRzdEVnMlRucXU1dnBnV2tpY1BZZy8wP3d4X2ZtdD1qcGVn\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; width: auto !important;\" width=\"auto\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28.4444px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">竞赛获奖证书可以直接证明你在这个领域的能力，找相关的工作，用人单位还不会用你吗？</span></p>\n\n<section label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n<section class=\"_135editor\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\">\n<p><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9naWYvc2xNdlR6N1QwT0s4NmtsaWNDcjlOa2FPWjhVWTdLdzZla3BiNWFjNmxyeG5LZzJTdHZYZDdtTFN1eWtVTU9PWFR5M0MxQ0gyeTJwVTNFbXZQMXJ4M0JnLzA=\" title=\"音符动态简约分割线\" /></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">留言来说说你认为重要的证书吧~&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xcGljLmNuL21tYml6X2pwZy9pYTZwOUNYblViZmNaRm1jcWhiS1h3WGFqRmQzVW10amlhcmtLS1A1Y1V5aWJXaWJXYnhDQk5WcTRyS1pwcFlhMGZwSGNKQUdLaHdEVEppY1RSMUlYZjBaMFJ3LzA/d3hfZm10PWpwZWc=\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">编辑：阁主 &nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n</section>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1211945/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1211945\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章